'''喬丹·史考特·亞戴爾'''（{{lang-en|Jordon Scott Adell}}，{{bd|1999年|4月8日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的外野手，目前效力於洛杉磯天使。他在2020年登上大聯盟。
==職業生涯==
===小聯盟===
亞戴爾在2017年大聯盟選秀於第一輪第10順位被天使隊選走。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/prospects/2017?list=draft|title=MLB.com 2017 Prospect Watch|website=Major League Baseball|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206042948/http://m.mlb.com/prospects/2017?list=draft|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.baseballamerica.com/draft/tournament-stars-day-one-adell-stands/#AceYeUIAXdJKTIkY.97|title=Tournament of Stars Day One: Adell Stands Out - BaseballAmerica.com|date=June 22, 2016|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2017-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170819063223/http://www.baseballamerica.com/draft/tournament-stars-day-one-adell-stands/#AceYeUIAXdJKTIkY.97|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.wlky.com/article/ballards-adell-closing-in-on-major-decision/3847177|title=Ballard's Adell closing in on major decision|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205060908/https://www.wlky.com/article/ballards-adell-closing-in-on-major-decision/3847177|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.angels.mlb.com/news/article/235986794/angels-draft-jordon-adell-in-first-round/?topicId=27118136|title=Angels draft Jordon Adell in first round|website=Los Angeles Angels|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2017-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170809211656/http://m.angels.mlb.com/news/article/235986794/angels-draft-jordon-adell-in-first-round/?topicId=27118136|dead-url=no}}</ref>他從亞利桑那聯盟開啟職業生涯，後來升上新人聯盟球隊[[歐仁貓頭鷹|歐仁貓頭鷹]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666176#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|title=Jo Adell Stats, Highlights, Bio – MiLB.com Stats – The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=December 23, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205045739/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666176#/career/R/hitting/2017/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，他入選全明星未來之星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.courier-journal.com/story/sports/mlb/minors/2018/07/06/former-ballard-star-jo-adell-play-mlb-futures-game/763463002/|title=Former Ballard High star Jo Adell named to MLB's Futures Game roster}}</ref>這年他也從1A一路升上2A。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666176#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|title=Jo Adell Stats, Highlights, Bio – MiLB.com Stats – The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|publisher=MiLB.com|access-date=December 31, 2018|archive-date=2021-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205045739/http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=666176#/career/R/hitting/2018/ALL|dead-url=no}}</ref>2019年，他受邀參加大聯盟春訓。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/angels/news/jo-adell-among-angels-non-roster-invitees/c-303178632|title=Top 5 prospects among Angels' NRIs: Adell, Canning included with the 21 players to get the call|date=January 25, 2019|access-date=2021-01-27|archive-date=2019-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222095219/https://www.mlb.com/angels/news/jo-adell-among-angels-non-roster-invitees/c-303178632|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他開季就進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|url = http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/26224813/angels-top-prospect-adell-miss-10-12-weeks|title = Angels top prospect Adell to miss 10–12 weeks|date = March 11, 2019|access-date = 2021-01-27|archive-date = 2020-11-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124185612/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/26224813/angels-top-prospect-adell-miss-10-12-weeks|dead-url = no}}</ref>後來他在小聯盟繳出3成47的打擊率，再一次入選全明星未來之星賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/news/2019-futures-game-rosters?t=mlb-pipeline-coverage|title=Here are the 2019 Futures Game rosters|author=Jim Callis|website=MLB.com|date=June 28, 2019|access-date=June 28, 2019|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201083045/https://www.mlb.com/news/2019-futures-game-rosters?t=mlb-pipeline-coverage|dead-url=no}}</ref>8月1日，他成功升上3A。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=adell-000jo- |title=Jo Adell Minor & Fall Leagues Statistics & History |publisher=Baseball-Reference.com |access-date=November 9, 2019 |archive-date=2021-01-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210103112138/https://www.baseball-reference.com/register/player.fcgi?id=adell-000jo- |dead-url=no }}</ref>

球季結束後，亞戴爾參加了亞利桑那秋季聯盟。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/2019-arizona-fall-league-rosters-announced/ | title=2019 Arizona Fall League Rosters Announced | access-date=2021-01-27 | archive-date=2021-02-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205213758/https://www.baseballamerica.com/stories/2019-arizona-fall-league-rosters-announced/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>10月10日，他獲選美國隊徵召參加[[2019年世界棒球12強賽|2019年世界棒球12強賽]]。<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.usabaseball.com/news/usa-baseball-names-premier12-roster/c-311115688?tid=216632610 | title=USA Baseball Names Premier12 Roster | work=USA Baseball | date=October 10, 2019 | access-date=October 13, 2019 | archive-date=2020-08-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814142625/https://www.usabaseball.com/news/usa-baseball-names-premier12-roster/c-311115688/?tid=216632610 | dead-url=no }}</ref>他在那裡繳出打擊率3成94，另敲出3轟與5分打點的成績。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://premier12.wbsc.org/en/2019/team-stats/USA |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2019-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117133214/https://premier12.wbsc.org/en/2019/team-stats/USA |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://premier12.wbsc.org/en/2019/stats/leaders |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-01-27 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927072055/https://premier12.wbsc.org/en/2019/stats/leaders |dead-url=no }}</ref>

===洛杉磯天使===
====2020年====
8月4日，亞戴爾登上大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Anderson |first1=R.J. |title=Angels promote Jo Adell, the No. 2 prospect in baseball, per report |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/angels-promote-jo-adell-the-no-2-prospect-in-baseball-per-report/ |website=CBS Sports |access-date=5 August 2020 |archive-date=2021-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228170648/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/angels-promote-jo-adell-the-no-2-prospect-in-baseball-per-report/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在初登板便敲出大聯盟首安。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Torres |first1=Maria |title=Jo Adell singles in at-bat debut, Mike Trout homers in return in Angels’ win over Mariners |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/angels/story/2020-08-04/jo-adell-singles-at-bat-debut-mike-trout-homers-angels-win-over-mariners |website=Los Angeles Times |access-date=5 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023032657/https://www.latimes.com/sports/angels/story/2020-08-04/jo-adell-singles-at-bat-debut-mike-trout-homers-angels-win-over-mariners |dead-url=no }}</ref>8月29日，他敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Digiovanna |first1=Mike |title=Angels’ Jo Adell hits first two homers of career to highlight 16-3 rout of Mariners |url=https://www.latimes.com/sports/angels/story/2020-08-29/angels-jo-adell-hits-first-two-homers-of-career-to-highlight-16-3-rout-of-mariners |website=Los Angeles Times |access-date=29 August 2020 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202032621/https://www.latimes.com/sports/angels/story/2020-08-29/angels-jo-adell-hits-first-two-homers-of-career-to-highlight-16-3-rout-of-mariners |dead-url=no }}</ref>並且在同一天達成雙響砲的成就，最後他的菜鳥球季留下打擊率1成61，敲出3轟與7分打點的成績。
